ingredients_text: Sugar, cocoa butter, HAZELNUT praline (10%) (HAZELNUT, sugar, flavouring, emulsifier (lecithin (SOY))), dietary fiber (inulin), cocoa mass, dark biscuits (7%) (WHEAT flour, white filling (sugar, vegetable fat (coconut), palm), emulsifier (lecithin), natural vanilla flavour, acidity regulator (citric acid), sugar, glucose-fructose syrup, vegetable fat (palm), water, skimmed cocoa powder, raising agents (ammonium bicarbonate, sodium carbonates), WHEAT starch, salt, emulsifier (lecithin), flavoring (natural flavoring), rice powder (rice syrup, rice flour), skimmed cocoa powder, rice syrup, rice flour, emulsifiers (lecithin, lecithin (SOY), flavors (natural vanilla flavoring, natural cocoa flavoring), acidity regulators (potassium carbonate, sodium hydroxide).
